title: DDFP 434: Free Agency Update & QBs circa Super Bowl 50
itunes:title: DDFP 434: Free Agency Update & QBs circa Super Bowl 50
description:
Shek sits down with Handsome Hank to discuss Shek's recent trip to the NFL Combine in Indianapolis. Shek talks free agents as well as potential draft prospects. The guys then discuss the Los Angeles Clippers brand new mascot, and Shek lists just a few of his favorite mascots. Lastly, Shek releases his top QBs circa Super Bowl 50. Will Peyton Manning make the list? Did Hank really meet Leo DiCaprio? What is that on Shek's upper lip? Find out more on DDFP.
